Package common.connector

package common.connector
Interfaces and classes related to the IConnector.
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    IConnector
    Defines how one ChatApp instance can complete a connection to another and invite another to a chat room.
    INamedConnector
    A dyad that allows a ChatApp to get the instance name associated with another ChatApp without making a costly network call.
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    AConnectorDataPacketAlgoCmd<T extends IConnectorMsg>
    A type-narrowed extended visitor command, used to process a message sent to an IConnector.
    ConnectorDataPacket<T extends IConnectorMsg>
    A data packet used to contain a message sent to an IConnector.
    ConnectorDataPacketAlgo
    An extended visitor used to process a message sent to an IConnector, provided for type-narrowing purposes.
